04-14/ty-article/jordanian-air-force-shoots-down-iranian-drones-flying-to-israel/0000018e-da2c-d5ed-adcf-fbbe5a130000</link><description>该国北部靠近叙利亚的多个城市以及中南部地区的居民听到剧烈的空中活动</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 02:15:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/jordanian-air-force-shoots-down-iranian-drones-flying-to-israel/0000018e-da2c-d5ed-adcf-fbbe5a130000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗直接袭击以色列后，联合国秘书长对局势升级的危险“深感震惊”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/un-chief-deeply-alarmed-by-danger-of-escalation-after-iran-directly-attacks-israel/0000018e-da0b-d01b-abdf-fa7f6e1b0000</link><description>安东尼奥·古特雷斯表示，有关各方必须确保避免造成“中东多条战线上的重大军事对抗”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 01:52:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/un-chief-deeply-alarmed-by-danger-of-escalation-after-iran-directly-attacks-israel/0000018e-da0b-d01b-abdf-fa7f6e1b0000</guid></item><item><title>300 架无人机和导弹：伊朗对以色列的首次直接攻击是如何开始的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-14/ty-article/200-drones-and-missiles-how-irans-first-direct-attack-on-israel-began/0000018e-da2f-d01b-abdf-fa7f0c860000</link><description>一名 10 岁女孩在袭击中受重伤，伊朗誓言要为 4 月 1 日叙利亚空袭造成两名将军死亡的事件报仇。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 01:49:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-14/ty-article/200-drones-and-missiles-how-irans-first-direct-attack-on-israel-began/0000018e-da2f-d01b-abdf-fa7f0c860000</guid></item><item><title>应以色列要求，联合国安理会周日召开会议讨论伊朗袭击事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-14/ty-article/israel-requests-emergency-un-security-council-meeting-on-iran/0000018e-da22-df04-adae-fff238070000</link><description>以色列驻联合国大使吉拉德·埃尔丹称德黑兰对以色列的无人机和导弹袭击“对全球和平与安全构成严重威胁”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 01:39:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-14/ty-article/israel-requests-emergency-un-security-council-meeting-on-iran/0000018e-da22-df04-adae-fff238070000</guid></item><item><title>拜登返回华盛顿，誓言在伊朗发动袭击时“铁定”支持以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/biden-returns-to-washington-vows-ironclad-support-for-israel-as-iran-launches-attack/0000018e-da18-de1f-a38f-de3f9aab0000</link><description>拜登缩短周末行程，与内阁成员和其他美国高级官员会面，讨论伊朗对以色列的导弹和无人机袭击</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 01:14:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/biden-returns-to-washington-vows-ironclad-support-for-israel-as-iran-launches-attack/0000018e-da18-de1f-a38f-de3f9aab0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗官员警告称，如果以色列对前所未有的攻击作出回应，伊朗将做出“更严厉”的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/iranian-officials-warn-of-more-severe-response-if-israel-responds-to-attack/0000018e-d9d5-d01b-abdf-f9ff4ebb0000</link><description>伊朗国防部长警告称，任何允许以色列发动袭击的国家都将面临回应，伊朗驻联合国代表团警告美国“远离”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 00:32:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/iranian-officials-warn-of-more-severe-response-if-israel-responds-to-attack/0000018e-d9d5-d01b-abdf-f9ff4ebb0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击以色列：发射数百枚导弹，大部分被拦截；以色列誓言回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article-live/biden-doubles-down-on-iran-warning-dont-u-s-move-additional-assets-to-region/0000018e-d491-d161-ab8f-f4f583d30000</link><description>以色列国防军：从伊朗发射的200多枚导弹、无人机，大部分被拦截；以色列南部的军事基地遭受轻微损坏； 10岁女孩受重伤 ■ 据报道，美国、英国和约旦拦截无人机 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡与拜登总统就袭击事件进行交谈 ■ 拜登：将与七国集团领导人讨论对伊朗袭击的统一外交反应 ■ 联合国安理会将于应以色列要求于周日</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 23:17:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article-live/biden-doubles-down-on-iran-warning-dont-u-s-move-additional-assets-to-region/0000018e-d491-d161-ab8f-f4f583d30000</guid></item><item><title>“让我们的人民走”：数千名以色列人在特拉维夫集